===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|abhomynable}}, from {{der|en|fro|abominable}}, from {{der|en|LL.|abōminābilis||deserving abhorrence}}, from {{m|la|abōminor||abhor, deprecate as an ill omen}}, from {{m|la|ab||from, away from}} + {{m|la|ōminor||forebode, predict, presage}}, from {{m|la|ōmen||sign, token, omen}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|en|/əˈbɑm.ə.nə.bl̩/|/əˈbɑm.nə.bl̩/}}
* {{a|NZ}} {{IPA|en|/ɘˈbɔm.ɘ.nɘ.bɯ/}}
* {{audio|en|en-us-abominable.ogg|Audio (US, California)}}

